Tams, as the midterm season ends, we all deserve a good rest.
 
Watch out as we go around to know what the students want and deserve this post-midterm season.
 
Take care of yourself and have fun to stay motivated for the rest of the semester!

#ContinuityAndBeyond

Hosted by: Phoebe Nacar

message.text:
Tams, as the midterm season ends, we all deserve a good rest.
 
Watch out as we go around to know what the students want and deserve this post-midterm season.
 
Take care of yourself and have fun to stay motivated for the rest of the semester!

#ContinuityAndBeyond

Caption by: Micaella Domingo
Edited by: Alyssa Buenavides
Hosted by: Phoebe Nacar
Shot by: Hannah Donor
